definition: the fifth/fifth day of a month
ordinal number/day of a month/mark/sign/business establishment/size/ship suffix/horn (wind instrument)/bugle call/assumed name/to take a pulse/classifier used to indicate number of people
AA battery (PRC)/Taiwan equivalent: 三號電池|三号电池

sentences.english: Size 5 footballs which provided by the Organiser should be used in all matches.
sentences.chinese: 所有賽事均使用由大會提供之五號足球作賽。

sentences.english: The name of the spaceship is Shenzhou V.
sentences.chinese: 宇宙飛船的名字是“神舟五號”。

sentences.english: May I have a double room for Junes, please?
sentences.chinese: 請幫我預訂一間六月五號的雙人房。

sentences.english: Your train is waiting at Platform 5.
sentences.chinese: 你要坐的那列火車在第五號站臺。

sentences.english: It is exciting that we have succeeded in sending up Shenzhou V.
sentences.chinese: 我們成功地發射了神舟五號這件事情真令人興奮。

sentences.english: I'd like a No. 5 meal please. Medium-sized.
sentences.chinese: 請給我一個五號中號的套餐。

sentences.english: Don't jump the gun because they usually start distributing paychecks on the 15th.
sentences.chinese: 不要太早去，因爲他們通常十五號纔開始發薪水。

sentences.english: Metro Line 5 station and the community close the main entrance.
sentences.chinese: 地鐵五號線車站與社區正門近在咫尺。

sentences.english: It falls around April 5 of the Gregorian calendar.
sentences.chinese: 它是在陽曆四月五號前後。

sentences.english: Her birthday is September 15th Do you have a School Day?
sentences.chinese: 她的生日是九月十五號你們有校慶日嗎？

sentences.english: Please come on March 5 to worship the Lord and support Ellena.
sentences.chinese: 歡迎大家在三月五號來參加這崇拜並支持楊惠卿同學。

sentences.english: My flat is on the tenth floor in Building 5 on Redrose Road.
sentences.chinese: 我的公寓在紅梅路五號樓十樓。

sentences.english: So, I'm at Fifth in Broadway in New York City.
sentences.chinese: 它們會說我在紐約城裏的百老匯街五號。

sentences.english: I liked to walk up Fifth Avenue and pick out romantic women from the crowd.
sentences.chinese: 我喜歡在五號路上蹓躂，在人羣中選挑風流的女人。

sentences.english: Pack your bags and travel far and wide, thanks to Mars in Cancer: October 1-15.
sentences.chinese: 一號到十五號火星在巨蟹座，整好旅行包到處漫遊吧。

sentences.english: According to the Basketball Rules, the numbers of the sports shirts should be from 4 to 15.
sentences.chinese: 根據籃球比賽賽例，球衣號碼必須爲四至十五號。
